data.description:
Home has a desert landscape and outside was recently painted as of 07/2022. Inside painted as of 02/2023. Owner has taken immaculate care of the home and added a few upgrades from a brand New backyard with artificial grass, Brand New water filtration system (drinking water), Beautifully done laminate flooring throughout the home and stainless steel appliances that goes so well with the home's esthetic.

Monthly rent $2000. A refundable security deposit equivalent to first months rent of $2000. A non-refundable pet deposit $250. Tenant is responsible for all utilities. (light & water) First months rent and deposits are required to be paid in full prior to signing of lease and moving in. Non- furnished home!
